{"tid":1186991,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲打屋企有養摺耳貓","createTime":"2019-06-05T10:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T16:12:23.000Z","uid":248161,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c1fb257b70543d4977a22f97ff7e5e5fa5856360","tid":1186991,"uid":248161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:13:51.000Z","msg":"屋企有養隻歲幾既摺耳貓<br />\n成日想上網買零食俾佢果時都search到大把摺耳貓病既資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企隻衰貓成日都唔郁 剩係食同訓<br />\n上網search又個個話係因爲佢骨痛先唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打有養摺耳貓可以分享下<br />\n<br />\n利申：係啊哥朋友屋企唔養先收養既"},{"pid":"e5fc749c1b7f8175109b0fe8c7f5a049f1fdf17d","tid":1186991,"uid":225192,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:38:39.000Z","msg":"基本上摺耳天生就一身病<br />\n隻貓痛足一世"},{"pid":"fd31baba492a9a2e20d7d9f9a1098564935a1996","tid":1186991,"uid":26333,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"無養都知摺耳貓好撚多病。"},{"pid":"f6d7904597106abc80550b83693458219db39963","tid":1186991,"uid":162713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:42:21.000Z","msg":"與其買零食撚貓<br />\n不如拎舊錢買補品俾佢食啦<br />\n歲幾都仲細 由細食住補品大<br />\n希望佢無病無痛咁陪你啦<br />\n<br />\n話是話 圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f80c44c3c9810a01452bef635ed3bdd77d88a6c","tid":1186991,"uid":206337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T15:46:08.000Z","msg":"領養就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係唔好買呢啲貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7a62981a57ee1f089864d6bb3f6c672839b49d","tid":1186991,"uid":10453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"摺耳本身就係病徵，有病徵又點會無病？第時收尾嗰幾年等佢輸服啲去啦"},{"pid":"7f5ef7a8cd941a9