/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e70197cd221b866fcd4a5a1ed9699ca956d1444","tid":1186991,"uid":248161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f5ef7a8cd941a98bcbb81e0bf6b9d3e5c9a7906","tid":1186991,"uid":10453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:01:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>摺耳本身就係病徵，有病徵又點會無病？第時收尾嗰幾年等佢<span style=\"color: red;\">舒</span>服啲去啦</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:12:23.000Z","msg":"就係希望就算佢個出身係冇咁好 <br />\n但係佢喺我屋企呢段時間都可以舒舒服服 盡量少啲病痛"}]}